div.span:
User and target permanently swap held items. Works even if one of the Pokmon isn't holding anything. If either Pokmon is holding mail, this move will fail.
If either Pokmon has multitype or sticky hold, this move will fail.
If this move results in a Pokmon obtaining choice band, choice scarf, or choice specs, and that Pokmon was the latter of the pair to move this turn, then the move it used this turn becomes its chosen forced move. This applies even if both Pokmon had a choice item before this move was used. If the first of the two Pokmon gains a choice item, it may select whatever choice move it wishes next turn.
Neither the user nor the target can recover its item with recycle.
This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
